sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant vLLM as vLLM / Model Server

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer (optional)<br/>Content-Type: application/json
    Note over Gateway: Inject detector config<br/>from route definition<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: passthrough<br/>X-Forwarded-*: passthrough<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Inference request
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated completion
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run output detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response<br/>(with detections field)
    Note over Gateway: Check detections field:<br/>• Empty → return response as-is<br/>• Non-empty → substitute fallback_message
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>stream: true<br/>Optional mTLS
    loop SSE chunks
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: {chunk with delta}
        Note over Gateway: Parse SSE chunk:<br/>Check for detections<br/>Replace content if detected
        Gateway-->>Client: data: {chunk or fallback}
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: data: [DONE]

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 3: Detection Triggered (Fallback)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with detections populated
    Note over Gateway: Detection found!<br/>Substitute configured<br/>fallback_message into<br/>choices[].message.content
    Gateway-->>Client: Response with fallback_message<br/>(original content replaced)
